WEBVTT

00:00:57.400 --> 00:01:01.080
Now we are in a village called Bhavi.

00:01:01.080 --> 00:01:03.320
Schools, courtyard shelters, ration stores

00:01:03.320 --> 00:01:06.320
are present here
for the convenience of people.

00:01:06.320 --> 00:01:10.240
If you walk another two kilometers,
going through farmlands,

00:01:10.240 --> 00:01:14.440
you won’t believe that
you are still in Bhavi.

00:01:14.440 --> 00:01:16.610
This area has only three homes.

00:01:16.610 --> 00:01:20.340
In one of them lives a
59 years old widow Jangubai.

00:01:21.050 --> 00:01:25.350
No one has ever been to a school
from Jangubai’s family,

00:01:25.400 --> 00:01:28.200
nor have they ever seen a tubelight.

00:01:29.240 --> 00:01:32.190
In the beginning of the year,
Jangubai and her people